Contents
Presentation



My main objective is not to write
about music theory (there are many good books on this that you can use) but to spend my time
in writing software to help you on your music studies. But some texts are necesary, I don't have much time for writing texts and it takes a lot of time to prepare an eBbook. Therefore, I have decided to publish the
lessons as soon as I write them, instead of waiting until the whole book is finished. Therefore the 'Theory and harmony' eBook is not yet finished and is currently just a collection of lessons on music theory, to help you to do exercises in an ordered progression of knowledge and difficulty.
 


